 * Password protection (AES256+CTR+HMAC)
 * Gravatars (requires email addresses)
 * Optional authentication:
    * DONE: Direct auth off of a database table using HTTP digest auth.
    * Enforcement of presence of REMOTE_USER environment variable.
    * Autocreation of authenticated users.
    * Direct LDAP support.
 * Uploading and binary blob support.
 * A decent skin.
